message.content: I'm sorry to hear you're feeling this way. If you are experiencing thoughts of harming yourself, please reach out to a mental health professional or a crisis hotline for help. You are not alone and there are people who care about you and want to support you through this difficult time. Please call a mental health hotline or seek help from a therapist or counselor. Your life is valuable and there are resources available to help you cope with these feelings.
